name: Bingo Baby
description:
The story of five adults (and one baby) in a railroad town, and how their small world spins out of control.

Bingo Baby is a 72-page, full-color comic book, created by Donna Almendrala, Bill Bedard, Joseph Lambert, Amelia Onorato and Denis St. John under the editorial oversight of their former teacher, cartoonist Jason Lutes.
